metadata.name: WE THE PEOPLE.
metadata.description:
For every tyrant, there will be thousands of people who resist. for every one that they kill, there will be two that will rise instead. the ultimate power is in on our hands, we are the power. lets see how many can you kill?

*one of four "digital" Dystopian pieces that were banned by opensea because of my nationality. original pieces were burned by the artist on may 27th 2022 in protest of that action and were reminted and will remain here as a symbol against censorship and oppression in art forever.
